      "type(Q)-is-int-and-not-bool",
      "1<=R<=Q<=9007199254740991"
    ],
    "accounting_semantics": "The content-addressed accounting policy defines cost_units as a fixed full-reservation charge for one successfully completed owned offline invocation. It is not a monetary, token, CPU, RAM or provider-metered usage claim. Generic exceptions and incomplete attempts remain fully reserved for later reconciliation.",
